<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-PT">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MiseSync x Love & Pepper | Proposta de Parceria</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#82cb15',
                        darkBg: '#1A1E24',
                        cardBg: '#252A33',
                        muted: '#A1A1AA',
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        serif: ['Playfair Display', 'serif'],
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        html { scroll-snap-type: y mandatory; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        section { scroll-snap-align: start; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .glow { position: absolute; width: 600px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(130,203,21,0.06) 0%, rgba(26,30,36,0) 70%); border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; }
        .content-card { position: relative; z-index: 10; width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; }
        body { background-color: #1A1E24; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- SECTION 1: TITLE -->
    <section>
        <div class="glow -top-48 -right-48"></div>
        <div class="content-card text-center">
            <h3 class="text-primary uppercase tracking-[4px] font-semibold mb-6 text-sm md:text-base">Apresentação de Parceria Estratégica</h3>
            <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold mb-8">MiseSync x <br><span class="text-primary italic">Love & Pepper</span></h1>
            <p class="text-muted text-lg md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                A digitalização inteligente do teu fluxo de trabalho: da preparação de kits ao serviço em festivais.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-12 animate-bounce">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down text-primary text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: O DESAFIO -->
    <section class="bg-[#161a20]">
        <div class="content-card">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-12 border-l-4 border-primary pl-8">O Caos dos <span class="text-primary italic text-3xl md:text-5xl block mt-2">Bastidores</span></h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <p class="text-xl text-white font-light">Gerir múltiplas frentes — Kits, Eventos e Festivais — exige um esforço administrativo que consome o teu tempo criativo.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-6">
                        <li class="flex gap-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-primary text-xl mt-1"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="block text-white text-lg">Dispersão de Dados</strong>
                                <span class="text-muted">Encomendas no WhatsApp, receitas em Excel e pagamentos em papel.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-primary text-xl mt-1"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="block text-white text-lg">Logística de Festivais</strong>
                                <span class="text-muted">Dificuldade em registar vendas rápidas e controlar o stock em tempo real.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-primary text-xl mt-1"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="block text-white text-lg">Cálculo de Insumos</strong>
                                <span class="text-muted">Somar manualmente quantidades de ingredientes para dezenas de kits.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/5 grayscale-[30%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
                    <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/027/488/307/small_2x/shock-over-bookkeeping-by-female-chef-and-restaurant-owner-sitting-over-paperwork-photo.jpg" alt="Caos Administrativo na Cozinha" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: CONCEITO -->
    <section>
        <div class="glow bottom-0 left-0"></div>
        <div class="content-card text-center">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-16 text-center">O Teu Negócio, <span class="text-primary italic">A Tua Marca</span></h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-cardBg p-10 rounded-2xl border-t-4 border-white shadow-xl">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-3xl mb-6"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-4 text-white">O Teu Frontend</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Marca Love & Pepper</p>
                    <p class="text-muted">O teu portal personalizado onde o cliente faz o pedido. A tua identidade visual mantém-se intacta e profissional.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-cardBg p-10 rounded-2xl border-b-4 border-primary shadow-xl">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-server text-primary text-3xl mb-6"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-4 text-white">O Nosso Backend</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">O Motor MiseSync</p>
                    <p class="text-muted">A tecnologia invisível que organiza os teus pedidos, gera listas de compras e controla as vendas de balcão.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4: MÓDULOS -->
