        <div class="content-card">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-12 text-center">O <span class="text-primary italic">Caminho</span></h2>
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 bg-cardBg p-4 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary shadow-lg">
                    <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-darkBg flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Acordo de Parceria (Hoje)</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Definição do estatuto de Laboratório e Permuta.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 bg-cardBg p-4 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-white/10">
                    <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-darkBg text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-white/20">2</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Mapeamento de Processos</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Questionário técnico para detalhar como geres as compras e vendas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 bg-cardBg p-4 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-white/10">
                    <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-darkBg text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-white/20">3</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">A Branch 'Beta'</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Primeiros testes reais na cozinha e nos próximos festivais.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 bg-cardBg p-4 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-white/10">
                    <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-darkBg text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-white/20">4</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Lançamento Oficial</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Transição para misesync.com com a tua conta vitalícia ativa.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 7: FINAL CALL -->
    <section>
        <div class="glow top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
        <div class="content-card text-center">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-7xl mb-12">Vamos digitalizar o <br><span class="text-primary italic">Mise en Place?</span></h2>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 leading-relaxed">
                Tu manténs o foco na arte dos teus pratos. Eu garanto a tecnologia que organiza a Love & Pepper.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
                <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSczdzu48HwJPvUcPcvbtIpd4nKoATeIsWOH1F8HMn9xmT0T-Q/viewform?usp=preview" target="_blank" class="bg-primary text-darkBg font-bold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg hover:scale-105 transition-all text-xl uppercase tracking-widest shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(130,203,21,0.2)]">Avançamos?</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-20">
                <a href="index.html" class="group text-muted hover:text-primary transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                    <span class="uppercase tracking-[4px] text-xs font-semibold">Visite o nosso website:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold border-b border-muted group-hover:border-primary">misesync.com</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
